Metadata: University of California Sea Grant San Diego County Cooperative Extension

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover articles include: Fishermen's safety survey, San Diego Bay Symposium, Third National Conference of Applied Marina Research, Boat waste management plans.
